commit.message:
Add rainfall_cleaner package with cleaning, io, and plotting modules

Extracts notebook logic into typed, documented functions:
clean_text_columns, parse_dates, normalize_numeric, deduplicate (cleaning.py);
load_raw, save_cleaned, save_summary, clean_rainfall pipeline (io.py);
plot_rainfall (plotting.py).  Public API re-exported from __init__.py.

